ingredientsDesc:
Anti-TPO Ab Test Units:
coated with highly purified human TPO.
Anti-TOP Ab Reagent Wedges:
LTOA: one wedge (6.5 mL) of buffer matrix.

Thyroid Autoantibody Sample Diluent:
100 mL anti-TG/anti-TPO antibody-free buffer matrix.
